[[File:Mage_tower_repaint_256.png|right]]The '''Moonglow Tower''' is a building in [[Lord of Ultima]]. It allows recruitment of caster units and, if upgraded, increases their recruitment speed. Also enables purification of resources for research, vital when recruiting Barons. Placing a Barracks beside a Moonglow Tower will also increase recruitment speed.

'''Requirements:''' [[Town Hall]] Level 7

